task.summary: Default task
Added TODOs
Fixed bug in SelfPlayLogsToPythonDataStructure. Added new methods and format for HumanReadableBoardPrinting
properly named main method. Exchanged threading with multiprocessing; much better performance. 50 minutes vs 5 hours. Could be further reduced by enumerating the files vs their directories.
added functionality to generate game visualizations via http://www.trmph.com/breakthrough/board#8,
removed unused imports
added transition vector computation for policy net data
redid mirror states to account for the transition vector
fixed bugs
mirror states now computed from mirrorMoveList instead of reflection of original states
reordered where program mirrors states, put mirror visualization URLs, mirrorMoveList in 'Games' dictionary, more comments/self-commenting code
added TODO
pulled mirrorstates to game entry, made GenerateBoardStates and Generate1dArraymore general. refactored FormatMoveList. turned GenerateBinaryPlane logic into dicts

added POVStates for policy net training data (white is original, black sees a reflected board state), made special conversion to 1d array for POV states (Player/Opponent/Empty & transition vector). normal states can still be used for a value net (each state of a game with a win value; consecutive white/black games will have the same states, but opposite win values).
added policy net stuff for NumpyArray
robust code branches added
corrected path names in aggregate lists
changed diskWrite path to go to the DataStructure directory directly
pipelined the conversion from txt to Numpy array
updated TODOs
changed 1d array to be list of one hot states
changed Numpy conversion to account for one hot boards
fixing NumpyArray bugs due to data representation changes
fixed by flattening out matrix again, but now in NumpyArray
refactoring pep8 starting from self-play to python data structures
Datastructures to DataStructures
continuing refactor by hand
refactored all function/variable names
better readability

used pandas to maintain and convert 2d planes for CNN; will reshape later

deprecation warnings for pd dataframe related coded, made list indexing more idiomatic, made numpy conversion row x column x feature plane for CNN
